name: Rustic Lantern Wedding Invitation and RSVP Postcard - Set of 25
description:
Dreaming of a rustic wedding in a barn or park? This invitation suite is a perfect way to introduce your theme.

Each invitation set includes: 
• one 5" x 7" wedding invitation (the back will be white unless you chose to upgrade to a matching colored backer) 
• one 5.5" x 4.25" two-sided RSVP postcard 
• one bright white A7 envelope 
• all items are digitally printed on bright white, smooth 110 lb. paper with a matte finish

Ready to order? 
• Select the quantity of invitation sets you would like. If you would like the back printed, please select the quantity + backer option. 
• Once you place an order, you will be contacted regarding the text you would like to appear on the invitation and RSVP card.
• The wording is up to you! The formatting will be the same or very similar to the image you see here.
• You will receive up to two rounds of edits. Additional changes can be made at $25 per revision. 
• You invitations will ship in 2-3 weeks after your order has been placed.

Want this design in a different color combination? 
No problem! The colors can be changed to your lovely wedding colors for an additional $25. This will be invoiced after your has been placed.
